session_summary: Tim and John caught up at 2:52 pm on 31 August, 2023. Tim shared his job rejection but remained positive. John discussed his NYC trip and troubles with the subway. Tim mentioned overcoming nerves to give a presentation. John shared his cooking experiment with a sage-flavored soup. Tim planned a trip to Universal Studios for the first time, excited for the Harry Potter attractions. They ended the conversation with well-wishes and a promise to catch up soon.

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Hey John, it's been a few days! I got a no for a summer job I wanted which wasn't great but I'm staying positive. On your NYC trip, did you have any troubles? How did you handle them?

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Hey Tim! Sorry to hear about the job, but your positivity will help you find something great! My trip went okay - I had some trouble figuring out the subway at first, but then it was easy after someone helped explain it. How about you? Anything new you've tackled?

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Thanks! Appreciate your encouragement. Yesterday, I tackled something new - I gave a presentation in class. I was nervous but I made it. Small step, but feels like progress.

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.blip_caption: a photo of a bowl of soup with a spoon and a butternut on a cutting board
conversation_turns.text: Cool, Tim! Taking the plunge and presenting can be tough, but awesome work! Progress is progress, keep it up. By the way, I've been trying out cooking recipes. Made this tasty soup recently - it was real good!

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Wow, that looks great! How did you make it? Do you have a recipe you can share?

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Thanks, I just sort of made it up on the spot so I don't have a recipe.

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: That's ok! I can look some up. Can you tell me what spices you used in the soup?

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: I added some sage for a nice flavor. Enjoy!

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Thanks! Excited to try this. Love experimenting with spices. By the way, have you been to Universal Studios? Planning a trip there next month.

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Cool! Haven't been there yet, but I've heard great things about Universal Studios. It's definitely on my bucket list. Have you been before?

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Nope, but it's my first time going. I'm super stoked for the Harry Potter stuff. Can't wait!

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Cool! It's gonna be a blast, like stepping into another world. Have a great time!

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Thanks! I'll definitely have a blast. I'll let you know how it goes!

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Great! Can't wait to hear about it. Have a safe trip!

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Thanks! I'll make sure to have a safe trip.

conversation_turns.speaker: John
conversation_turns.text: Bye! Take care and let's catch up soon!

conversation_turns.speaker: Tim
conversation_turns.text: Take care! Can't wait to catch up. Talk soon!
